                Game game,
                javax.swing.ImageIcon image)
        Parameters:
        x - X location on the Gameboard
        y - Y location on the Gameboard
        width - width of border collision rectangle (typically width of the image)
        height - height of border collision rectangle (typically height of the image)
        solid - True if Characters cannot walk through it
        breakable - True if Mario can break it
        game - The instance of the Game
        image - The ImageIcon representing the Obstacle
